        - Isreal/Palestine 
        - Iran movement
    Good Communities:
        - find metric for a "good" community.
            - double edge swap vs cluster coeficient, p value
            - size, date, degree, etc
            - mean upvotes corolations
            - average period
            - mean posts
            - weight of graphs
            - how many links are reciprocal
        - scrape multiple sides -> find best community



